==English==

===Noun===
'''leptonema'''

# A [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]] belonging to the [[family]] ''[[Phyllanthaceae]]''.
# The [[stage]] during [[meiotis]] [[Prophase 1]] where the [[chromosome]]s condense after S-phase and interphase, resulting in the recombination of haploid chromosome pairs with sister chromatids held by a single non-dividing centromeres, and followed by the Zygotene stage.